      res.success
        ? `You turn a blade to the torchlight and your stomach drops. Struck into the ricasso, plain as a signature: the <b>anvil-and-tower of the Ironvale city forge</b>. This steel was made INSIDE the walls you're fighting for — and shipped here in crates. <b>(EVIDENCE: forge-marked steel — you wrap a shortsword to keep.)</b>`
        : `Good steel, strangely uniform — but the maker's marks mean nothing to you, and there's no time to puzzle over smith-craft.`,
      `A coin chest by the door yields <b>40 gold</b>.` ],
    [ { txt: "← Back to the junction", onclick: `C.gold += 40; ${res.success ? "addEvidence('forgemark');" : ""} logRoll('💰','+40 gold from the cache','success'); goScene('m2_warren')` } ]);
